data.description: Welcome Home! 13 Panel Solar is completely PAID OFF.  Beautiful end of Cul-de-sac home in the center of Menifee. Located on Banner Park Community which has its own pavilion, basketball courts, splash pad, and more. As you enter the 6 bedroom, 4 1/2 bath home you will be greeted by high ceilings, recessed lighting, and ceiling fans throughout the home. The multi-generation floor plan features a suite right off the entrance, great for guests with an extra flex room that is great for an office or sitting area. The living room is a spacious entertainment area with a large glass slider to the backyard and is also open to a beautiful Chef’s kitchen. The kitchen features White Quartz counters, eat-up bar island, pendant lights, high end KitchenAid stainless steel appliances featuring dual oven plus convection oven, 5 burner stove, hood, deep stainless steel farm sink with modern cabinets and large walk-in pantry. Second bedroom is also downstairs with its own bathroom. Second floor features a spacious loft, 3 secondary bedrooms that share a large secondary bath boasting a dual vanity and soaking tub shower combo. The expansive master bedroom with attached bath featuring standing shower, soaking tub, dual vanity, and large walk-in closet. The backyard was built for gatherings with its ample space perfect for entertaining, 3 outdoor ceiling fans, concrete floors and low maintenance landscaping with green turf. The property is located just minutes from the 215 freeway, 20 minutes to the Temecula wineries, close to shopping, restaurants and much more!
